Begin treestumpScript

short setonce

if ( OnActivate == 0 )
	return
endif

if ( GetJournalIndex "MS_Lookout" >= 20 )
	if ( GetJournalIndex "MS_Lookout" < 40 )
		if ( fargothwalk >= 2 )
			if ( setonce == 0 )
				Journal "MS_Lookout" 40
				set setonce to -1
			endif
		endif
	endif
endif

Activate

End treestumpScript
